{"tid":801994,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"而家邊到有平保齡球場","createTime":"2018-09-01T06:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T16:03:45.000Z","uid":31426,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"44eca7b89c49eb553ddfd3a9e7e20f1a72fe797f","tid":801994,"uid":31426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:09:08.000Z","msg":"小弟住粉嶺  就咁google完之後<br />\n最近間碌ling場都要起沙田富豪<br />\n查多兩查  原來碌ling咁撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一局都收你$3X-$4X 其實就好快完一局<br />\n想問下香港啲ling場都係得番呢啲  無乜場可以選擇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搭單問埋  何文田間ling埸好耐之前好似轉咗老闆  收咗皮一排<br />\n依家開返未<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd21532a9a958c7ea69e51273aaf5ae9f6ba8a09","tid":801994,"uid":133727,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:11:16.000Z","msg":"窮撚留係屋企碌水樽啦"},{"pid":"3f3ed000ae2b1e6c7cb5e13068430eeff15e4a17","tid":801994,"uid":60689,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:12:20.000Z","msg":"去冒險樂園玩啦窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f04cf2c2baa7ff61b3a89f0004406fbebad681b","tid":801994,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:13:30.000Z","msg":"利申：會所10蚊一場"},{"pid":"e35998dfd744ceef86c9f97e5ccaad43d7d20783","tid":801994,"uid":119302,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:14:30.000Z","msg":"認真答你，屯門美樂有<br />\n價錢無記錯正價好似90一個鐘<br />\n最多可以8個人一條ling <br />\n利申以前用學生証日日去打，38蚊一個鐘"},{"pid":"bf22b38f4f2869b1b3493eb74a7bed1a1232e655","tid":801994,"uid":103936,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"bd21532a9a958c7ea69e51273aaf5ae9f6ba8a09","tid":801994,"uid":133727,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:11:16.000Z","msg":"窮撚留係屋企碌水樽啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3 40蚊一餐飯價錢<br />\n條ling咁撚長 平日又冇人玩<br />\n場租都要啦屌<br />\n搞手都係打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e78946cdff5ad20954be68f504da4dba23817d5","tid":801994,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"荃灣咪有間"},{"pid":"98b56bd124a4fbd9c8d1984447f82e5cce42e3a2","tid":801994,"uid":31426,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bd21532a9a958c7ea69e51273aaf5ae9f6ba8a09","tid":801994,"uid":133727,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:11:16.000Z","msg":"窮撚留係屋企碌水樽啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T07:49:02.000Z","msg":"鬼唔知連登仔個個都月入50K咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我話貴 就屌我窮 邊粒字話你聽我比唔起<br />\n問下邊到有無平啲都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n他日$100碗紅豆沙 你話貴 人地笑鳩你食唔起添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nChild登真係無改錯名  係唔係都即刻駁嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e948d18368fbf2a05d99c592b4740c474405da7","tid":801994,"uid":31426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e35998dfd744ceef86c9f97e5ccaad43d7d20783","tid":801994,"uid":119302,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:14:30.000Z","msg":"認真答你，屯門美樂有<br />\n價錢無記錯正價好似90一個鐘<br />\n最多可以8個人一條ling <br />\n利申以前用學生証日日去打，38蚊一個鐘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T07:50:06.000Z","msg":"搵下先, thx for sharing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b8bdf86511fe751c06fa67632e87f9c0c2f1a1","tid":801994,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T07:52:47.000Z","msg":"沙田果間貴撚到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 碌過一次之後都唔去<br />\n荃灣迪高平好多"},{"pid":"8a7dd22458e2163dee37c74adb0d51934d556254","tid":801994,"uid":119302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e948d18368fbf2a05d99c592b4740c474405da7","tid":801994,"uid":31426,"li